= v2.3 =
 * Added patches by Robin Schneider.
 * Parsing of options in config files improved.
 * Coding style improvements.

= v2.2a =
 * Added support for config files in local, program and user directory as well as in the texmf tree.
 * Updated documentation and provided it as man page and PDF.
 * Added support for keys defined by `keyval` and the `xkeyval` packages.
 * Added -r/-R options to remove existing code environments.
 * Fixed missing support for starred environments.
 * Added support for `--help` and `-help` switch.
 * Added README.
 * Added support for additional output files.
 * Disabled new line removal after variables.
